data.description: Welcome home to this charming two-story residence in sought-after Mountain View neighborhood. Recent upgrades elevate this property, offering comfortable living. The updated kitchen features new kitchen cabinets, new LVP flooring, black appliances, granite countertops and French doors that open to the expansive fenced backyard with a playset. The family room with a gas fireplace is perfect for relaxation, while the spacious living room and dining area are ideal for entertaining. Upstairs, the Primary Suite boasts vaulted ceiling and dual walk-in closets. The primary bath is a retreat with a dual vanity, garden tub, shower, and water closet. Three more bedrooms and a full bath offer ample space for family and guests. The two-car finished garage provides generous space for storage, and has a side door for access to backyard. You don't want to miss this one!
